title: Hour 1 - Vanilla Ice Cream, Chris Simms
itunes:title: Hour 1 - Vanilla Ice Cream, Chris Simms
description:
Dan compares tonight's Thursday Night Football Game between the Indianapolis Colts and Denver Broncos to an ice cream party only serving plain vanilla. And he talks to former NFL QB and current analyst Chris Simms about playing with injuries in the NFL.
